author: Michael Thompson
title: Michael Thompson
text: I ordered my supplies on a Tuesday night and was at my door by Friday everything I ordered bubble wrapped and the quality of the mixing flavors are second to no one. There's flavors are very balanced not to weak and not to strong. This is the only place I would recommend with 100% of my confidence they will enjoy it.
